name: Super Maze
description: One of my favorite acrylic paintings from 2020 with some subtle hue changes. Titled "Super Maze". It reminds me of going to the doctor's office as a kid and playing with those twisty sculpture thingies. Authentic, original work by Kris Kanaly, aka Pyramid Guy. Minted by Kris Kanaly on 5/18/2021, Â©2021 Kris Kanaly. Original painting has sold.
